Name: Invoke: Javelin
Desc:
Throws a sharp magic javelin that attacks while flying between enemies.It prioritizes tracking Boss Monsters with the highest Max HP.
It can be linked with Invoke: Orb, and it does not affect skill enhancement effects from multi-target skills.
Lv. 20 Effect: Can learn 2nd Job Skill, Reaction: Destruction, and 4th Job Skill, Invoke: Javelin II.
